    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps identified at MRL 5, the assessment team accepted the package for submission on the basis that the Monte Carlo UQ bounds remain below the absolute clinical hemolysis threshold across all assessed operating conditions. Remaining epistemic gaps are flagged for resolution in subsequent assessment cycle prior to regulatory submission.",
